metrics.description: Array with one item per requested metric. Each item is an array of values, broken down by time interval.

items.description: Nominal metric values, broken down by time interval.

time_intervals.description: Array of time intervals in the response data. Each interval is represented as an array containing two values: the start time, and the end time.

items.description: Array with exactly two items, representing the start and end time (respectively) of this time interval.
